  ('I want to save up for a trip, but I never actually stick to a savings goal.', 'A simple goal tracker where I set a target amount and date, and it tells me how much to set aside each week to get there.', '1b3b2d99-cd41-4f8b-9805-63155203ff81', '2026-06-05T12:00:00Z'),
  ('Splitting bills with roommates always turns into a confusing group chat full of who-owes-who.', 'A shared list where we log shared expenses and it automatically calculates who owes what to whom.', '1b3b2d99-cd41-4f8b-9805-63155203ff81', '2026-06-07T12:00:00Z'),
  ('I don''t really know where my money goes each month, I just know it''s gone.', 'A simple way to log purchases by category and see a breakdown at the end of the month.', '1b3b2d99-cd41-4f8b-9805-63155203ff81', '2026-06-08T12:00:00Z'),
  ('I want to compare prices before buying something big, but I forget what I found on different sites.', 'A place to paste in links and prices I''m comparing, so I can see them side by side before deciding.', '1b3b2d99-cd41-4f8b-9805-63155203ff81', '2026-06-10T12:00:00Z'),
  ('I have a vague savings goal for a new laptop but no plan, so I never actually save.', 'A visual progress bar for a savings goal, plus a quick way to log how much I saved today.', '1b3b2d99-cd41-4f8b-9805-63155203ff81', '2026-06-11T12:00:00Z'),
  ('I have tasks scattered across notes apps, texts, and my memory, so things fall through the cracks.', 'One simple list where I can dump anything I need to do and check it off, without folders getting in the way.', '1b3b2d99-cd41-4f8b-9805-63155203ff81', '2026-06-13T12:00:00Z'),
