  ('I set goals at the start of the week but never check back in on them.', 'A weekly check-in screen that shows my goals from Monday and asks me to mark them done or carried over.', '1b3b2d99-cd41-4f8b-9805-63155203ff81', '2026-06-19T12:00:00Z'),
