  ('I have too many browser tabs open with things I meant to read or do later.', 'A place to save a link with a one-line note about why I saved it, so my browser tabs can stay closed.', '1b3b2d99-cd41-4f8b-9805-63155203ff81', '2026-06-22T12:00:00Z'),
